official_title: A bill providing for a feasibility study of certain highways for the purpose of including such highways in the National System of Interstate and Defense Highways.

summary.text: Provides for a feasibility study of specified highways from Brunswick, Georgia, or its vicinity to Kansas City, Missouri, or its vicinity for the purpose of including such highways in the National System of Interstate and Defense Highways.

titles.title: A bill providing for a feasibility study of certain highways for the purpose of including such highways in the National System of Interstate and Defense Highways.
